data.description: Welcome to a house that you can make your home.   This house is centrally located. Its impeccable curb appeal is distinguished by the remarkably landscaped gated front lawn equipped with elegant wrought iron railings. Enjoy a quiet afternoon on a spring day on your welcoming front porch or night cap while reading a book under the porch light. Feel the extra comfort and peace of mind with a brand-new security door.   This house provides you with an open concept gorgeously modernized with granite kitchen, all new stainless-steel appliances, and a decorative and distinctive backsplash. Attached to the kitchen is an enclosed charming pantry perfect for bonus storage.   All new energy efficient windows throughout the house. Take a nice relaxing bath or refreshing shower with your skylight open to allow a gentle breeze on a warm summer day. Each bedroom is equipped with a new ceiling fan and pristine hardwood floors. Extra closet space and storage in your lengthened hallway.    Basement is unfinished but can be easily transformed into the perfect laundry room, workout room, child playroom or rec room. Don’t overlook the renovated powder room appropriately situated in the basement.  Walk out into your gated backyard which is awaiting your unique touch to turn this into your ideal outdoor living space where you can have summer barbecues or winter bon fires. There’s plenty of space for seating, a grill, a fire pit and so much more.   Don’s miss out! Schedule a showing today…this house is likely to sell fast!
